    <!-- Introduction -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
        When your business needs reliable, high-quality packaging solutions, new carton boxes are the gold standard. Whether you're shipping products across Malaysia, protecting goods in storage, or expanding your logistics operations, choosing the right new carton boxes can make a significant difference in product safety, brand presentation, and overall cost-efficiency. Quinocycle Sdn. Bhd., based in Balakong, Selangor, has been supplying premium new carton boxes to businesses across Peninsular Malaysia since 2010.
