      </p>

      <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mt-6 mb-3">Double-Wall Corrugated Boxes</h3>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Double-wall carton boxes provide superior strength and protection with two layers of fluted material. These boxes are built to withstand heavy loads, rough handling, and long-distance shipping. Industries such as furniture manufacturing, automotive parts distribution, and food production rely heavily on double-wall boxes. While slightly more expensive than single-wall options, their durability and protective qualities make them invaluable for high-value or fragile items. Quinocycle offers double-wall boxes at competitive wholesale rates.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mt-6 mb-3">Custom Printed Carton Boxes</h3>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Many businesses benefit from custom-printed carton boxes that feature brand logos, product information, handling instructions, and barcode printing. While Quinocycle specializes in standard new boxes, custom printing services can be arranged for bulk orders, enhancing brand visibility and professionalism during shipment.
      </p>
    </section>

